# Hallo {{{

IMAPAccount hallo-account
Host imap.gmail.com
User hallo@kaiec.de
Port 993
PassCmd "gpg --no-tty -q -d ~/.kak/hallo.gpg"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt


IMAPStore hallo-remote
Account hallo-account

MaildirStore hallo-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/Maildir/hallo/
Inbox ~/Maildir/hallo/Inbox
Flatten "."

Channel hallo
Master :hallo-remote:
Slave :hallo-local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]*
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

# }}}

